Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.98,0:02:13.99,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an4\c&H1A1A1A&\pos(565,475)}海底的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.97,0:23:40.98,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\an4\c&H1A1A1A&\pos(205,475)}重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.03,0:00:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我們為了探索梅爾基涅海底遺跡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.60,0:00:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,決定暫時離開愛尼森
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.80,0:00:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,始？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.23,0:00:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,梅爾基涅海底遺跡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.37,0:00:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,應該就在這附近才對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.53,0:02:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,自然風景不論在哪都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.57,0:02:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就像在日本的海邊見過的夕陽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.93,0:02:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,總感覺很懷念 明明才過了半年不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.07,0:02:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟在這邊每天都過得不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.30,0:02:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.43,0:02:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,始大人 你在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.00,0:02:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那個應該是古盧恩攻略證明吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.13,0:03:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.10,0:03:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,光都聚集起來了 真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.77,0:03:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,對啊 真神奇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.20,0:03:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,真是不錯的演出
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,完全不像另外某個白痴解放者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.50,0:03:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,就是啊 很夢幻 我都有點感動了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此 難怪一直找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.67,0:04:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,本來還想靠運氣找到入口 太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.63,0:04:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,水流真急啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.30,0:04:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,又要被沖到其他地方了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.47,0:04:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,0:04:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,後方有什麼東西在靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,從纏繞的紅黑色魔力來看肯定是魔物了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.03,0:04:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,正好試試我的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.53,0:04:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好 威力比之前更大了 改良成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.70,0:05:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,始大人 那裡也有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.83,0:05:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是第五個了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.50,0:05:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,五芒星的紋章和五個印記
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,以及留存著光的項鍊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.00,0:05:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,光靠魔法想來這裡可不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,如果不能儘早察覺線索 魔力就不夠用了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.77,0:05:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,得感謝主人這艘船啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.43,0:05:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.43,0:05:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,看來好戲這才正式開場啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:06:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,與其說是海底遺跡 根本就是個洞窟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.67,0:06:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,還好不是完全泡在水裡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.83,0:06:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,月
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.87,0:06:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,交給月吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.97,0:06:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.37,0:06:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.77,0:06:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,頂上好像有什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,這是搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.40,0:06:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,月
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,始 說實話有點害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.97,0:07:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,水也慢慢變深了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.80,0:07:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣你也更輕鬆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.97,0:07:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,話是這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.33,0:07:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,月大人 總感覺有點可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.57,0:07:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,最近代替繆的位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.97,0:07:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那以後就叫你小月月怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.80,0:07:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,去死吧 香織
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼對我這麼刻薄
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.57,0:07:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 不覺得太弱了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.40,0:07:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,太弱了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.87,0:07:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 作為大迷宮的魔物而言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.60,0:07:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.67,0:07:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.70,0:08:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.30,0:08:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,希婭 別亂動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.00,0:08:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 始大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.67,0:08:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我燙傷了 能幫我塗藥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.00,0:08:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道現在什麼狀況嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,月大人和緹奧大姐雙管齊下 應該沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.07,0:08:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,賜予聖淨與治癒 天惠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好不容易有機會被摸胸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.77,0:08:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,始 這布丁好像能溶解魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.07,0:08:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,果然如此 剛剛我就奇怪火焰怎麼被削弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.03,0:08:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,看來連火焰裡的魔力也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.93,0:09:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.93,0:09:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,終於有點大迷宮的樣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.50,0:10:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,月也去攻擊 我負責防禦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.63,0:10:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,聖絕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.53,0:10:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒完
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.10,0:10:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,這到底是什麼啊 整個空間都有魔物反應
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是大迷宮的魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.70,0:10:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,主人 不能讓它無限再生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,魔石在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.73,0:10:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,說起來 明明是透明的卻看不見魔石
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.63,0:10:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.60,0:10:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有 它沒有魔石
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.03,0:10:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有魔石…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.80,0:11:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是說它不是魔物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.13,0:11:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,在我的魔眼石看來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.10,0:11:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,它的身體全都是紅黑色的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,就像布丁狀的整個身體 都是一塊魔石
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.17,0:11:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,整個身體…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.67,0:11:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,整個空間都是同樣的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.50,0:11:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,說不定我們已經在它肚子裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.87,0:11:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,來吧 該開飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.87,0:11:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,沒完沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.77,0:11:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙真煩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.77,0:12:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,沒什麼辦法對付它嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.00,0:12:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,重整一下隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,地下還有空間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然不知道通向什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.90,0:12:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,做好心理準備
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:13:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧 香織
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.23,0:13:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,還好 大家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.63,0:13:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.03,0:13:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然是小倉庫級別
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.53,0:13:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,她們每個人我都給了寶物庫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.33,0:13:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,她們自己會想辦法的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.40,0:13:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 始
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.30,0:13:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你為什麼救我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.27,0:13:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,突然問這個幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.27,0:13:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼你不去救月 而是救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,因為香織都快沒命了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,但是月自己能想辦法撐過去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,她還用眼神教訓我了 讓我來救你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.77,0:13:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你很信任她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.47,0:13:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那還用說 我們可是搭檔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.57,0:13:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛 你幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.90,0:13:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,有空在這裡垂頭喪氣 不如行動起來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.40,0:13:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡可是大迷宮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是發了會兒呆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.57,0:14:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.93,0:14:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.77,0:14:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,只能朝深處進發 繼續探索了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.23,0:14:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,月她們也會這麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.60,0:14:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,也對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.03,0:14:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,算是船的亂葬崗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.70,0:14:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,全都是戰艦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.73,0:14:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不過 那艘最大的船感覺不太一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.80,0:14:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,有點像客船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.93,0:14:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.50,0:14:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,始 看周圍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.93,0:15:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我這是在做夢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.88,0:15:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.10,0:15:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我來防禦 光絕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.70,0:15:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,原來是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.47,0:15:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,看來這不僅是幻覺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.97,0:15:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但也不是現實
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.33,0:15:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.50,0:15:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,有實體的攻擊不起作用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,但是帶有魔力的攻擊有用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.63,0:15:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 到底是怎麼搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.87,0:15:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.63,0:16:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,只要帶有魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.17,0:16:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,屬性和效果一律都算攻擊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.87,0:16:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那我 把他殺了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.13,0:16:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是現實
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.00,0:16:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,就當是能直接觸碰到的幻覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.40,0:16:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我有點慌了 不過現在沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,老是道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.67,0:16:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.83,0:16:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,沒說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都是為了神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,埃希德大人萬歲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.77,0:16:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,異教徒 死在我們的神面前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.47,0:16:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,香織 我們跳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.13,0:17:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 到底怎樣才能逃離這個噁心的空間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,應該有出口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.17,0:17:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,說不定哪艘船就是出口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.53,0:17:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這裡可有幾百艘 怎麼可能一艘艘去找
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.27,0:17:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我倒是覺得結束這場戰爭反而更快
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.83,0:17:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那就…結束這場戰爭？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.30,0:17:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,結束？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.73,0:17:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此 總之先把他們都殺光怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.77,0:17:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是這個意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.37,0:17:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,這方案我喜歡 走吧 香織
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.57,0:17:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.13,0:17:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,始 那到底是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.53,0:17:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,和這些廢船有關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,用幻術之類的把以前的戰爭再現了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.73,0:17:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎加了一些改良 用來襲擊大迷宮的挑戰者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.87,0:17:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.83,0:17:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,說不定這就是這個大迷宮的主題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.87,0:17:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,主題？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.30,0:18:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,緹奧說過 每個大迷宮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.80,0:18:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,應該都有解放者們準備的主題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,如果真是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.43,0:18:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那這裡的主題…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.50,0:18:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,讓人知曉發瘋的神造成了什麼慘劇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.13,0:18:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,始 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.90,0:18:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,別在意 我明白快被瘋狂吞沒時的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.43,0:18:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟我在奈落之底也曾差點被吞沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.83,0:18:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,最後沒被吞沒 是因為月？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.13,0:18:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,如果沒遇到她 後果難以想像
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.47,0:18:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,好不甘心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.43,0:18:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,真希望留住你的人和守護你的人 都是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.73,0:19:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不過話說回來 我也不知道能做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.13,0:19:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,連一個約定也沒能遵守
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.97,0:19:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,月真是強敵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.40,0:19:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,來這裡之後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你動不動就道歉 苦笑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.70,0:19:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,香織
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.40,0:19:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你為什麼要跟我們來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.93,0:19:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.73,0:19:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,果然我還是礙事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.03,0:19:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.17,0:19:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得希婭怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.27,0:19:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,希婭？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.83,0:19:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,剛開始的時候 我對她很粗暴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.50,0:19:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我只在乎月
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.07,0:19:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我只希望她能早日放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.53,0:19:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,但是她一下生氣一下開心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.33,0:19:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,有時還會哭鼻子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.97,0:19:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,即便如此她也很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.83,0:20:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就算不能使用魔法 只會使蠻力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,她也從不會停下腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.00,0:20:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不會因自卑而屈服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.23,0:20:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我才沒覺得自卑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.37,0:20:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你發現了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.07,0:20:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,來這裡之後 你動不動就道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.53,0:20:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,連笑容都和以前不一樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.27,0:20:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,香織 別低頭
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.23,0:20:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,抬起頭來看著我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我再說一次 我喜歡月
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.90,0:20:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,就算我會很重視其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.20,0:20:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但也改變不了月在我心中的地位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.57,0:20:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,如果這個事實只會讓你覺得難受
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.40,0:20:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,如果和月相比只會讓你覺得自卑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,香織 那你最好還是離開我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.60,0:20:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,今天必須把非常重要的事告訴大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.43,0:21:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,初次見面 畑山愛子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.20,0:21:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我來接你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.20,0:21:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,初次見面 來接我是指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.43,0:21:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我得去和學生們吃晚餐了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.97,0:21:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,不 你要去的地方是神山
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.67,0:21:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.50,0:21:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.07,0:21:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是拋開主人自稱為神的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.43,0:21:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,居然能彈開我的魅了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.87,0:21:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.63,0:21:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.87,0:21:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,放心 不會殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.40,0:21:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你是顆優秀的棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.10,0:21:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.67,0:22:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,得告訴其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.00,0:23:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.16,0:01:01.71,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Tears streaming down your sorrow face
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.87,0:01:07.71,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Came a long and painful road, you gave yourself away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.55,0:01:13.05,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You saw everything, heaven to hell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:19.47,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You say you need a self redemption, to mend the broken wings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.98,0:01:24.90,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Drowning in the dark, no place to be
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.61,0:01:28.65,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}But I am by your side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.94,0:01:30.49,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You’re not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.74,0:01:36.41,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Daylight, shed a light so you won’t disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.62,0:01:42.37,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Cause I know where you belong, save your saddened heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.37,0:01:48.09,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}With a flashback, screaming out but still we’re holding on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.25,0:01:53.51,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Waiting for the break of dawn for a new day to begin
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.97,0:01:56.76,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Daylight, daylight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.35,0:02:02.10,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Stay a little while longer
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.39,0:22:12.73,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全部　期待してみて幻だった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.73,0:22:17.23,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}信じたかった　縋りたかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.15,0:22:23.95,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}身体の底に開いた螺旋状の穴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.24,0:22:29.12,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}ボクだけじゃなく　キミにもなんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.58,0:22:38.29,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}許されることなど　もう望んじゃいない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.29,0:22:42.84,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱き寄せてもまた　わからないシルエット
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.84,0:22:47.39,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}躊躇いもなく傷つけた代償か
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.64,0:22:52.52,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}キミの側は　揺れてボクを離れた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.52,0:22:57.48,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}どちらが欲しいかなんて　残酷な問い神様は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.48,0:23:02.07,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何度ボクらに投げかける
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.07,0:23:07.07,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}道を違える度に　ボクの後ろに穴が開く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.07,0:23:10.12,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}伸びた一本の影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.41,0:23:16.58,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誰もが手にし得る　小さな欠片で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.83,0:23:21.17,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何ができる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.17,0:23:26.34,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}どちらが欲しいかなんて　残酷な問い神様は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.34,0:23:31.18,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何度ボクらに投げかける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.39,0:22:12.73,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}期待的一切皆為虛空一場
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.73,0:22:17.23,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}破滅的希望　虛偽的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.15,0:22:23.95,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嵌入身體的傷口深不見底
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.24,0:22:29.12,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不僅是我　你也背負同樣的傷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.58,0:22:38.29,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早已不再奢望　求得誰人原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.29,0:22:42.84,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哪怕懷中相擁　徒留輪廓難辨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.84,0:22:47.39,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}甘願承傷不曾猶豫的代價
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.64,0:22:52.52,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我步履蹣跚　忍痛離開你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.52,0:22:57.48,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神明凜然在上　拋下兩難抉擇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.48,0:23:02.07,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不斷拷問你我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.07,0:23:07.07,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}幾步對錯　令我身負百孔千瘡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.07,0:23:10.12,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}形單影隻漸行漸遠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.41,0:23:16.58,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}希望碎片　誰人不曾擁有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.83,0:23:21.17,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}又能作何掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.17,0:23:26.34,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神明凜然在上　拋下兩難抉擇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.34,0:23:31.18,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不斷拷問你我
